{"tid":857653,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有心事嘅入嚟擺低 冇心事嘅入嚟吹水 (374) 召喚質素","createTime":"2018-10-11T08:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T18:16:57.000Z","uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c7feb3ff0d74bf615d6142297965a2ab6bd423a1","tid":857653,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:41:41.000Z","msg":"唔小心三百七十四咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續有心事入嚟擺低 無心事入嚟吹水<br />\n絕非小圈子 有心事就算見到吹緊水都唔使怕羞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時候有啲巴絲比既意見會比較直擊 大家唔好嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時有啲巴絲講野好低b 因為都係無聊野傾到冇野傾先講低b嘢<br />\n所以好歡迎新話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時候有啲巴絲會po啲好黑既嘢<br />\n又有時候會無啦啦變左成人台<br />\n如果你handle唔到可以唔理佢地<br />\nhandle唔到都無辦法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望多啲人討論歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋遷就唔識英文同日文嘅巴絲 唔該<br />\n但係希望大家唔好歌詞/藝人相洗版 咁會嚇親有心事既巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果見到有啲reply覺得唔係太舒服 請體諒呢個po大多都係有心事有情緒既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋大家都注意返 對啲有心事有情緒既巴絲 唔好講啲刺激性攻擊性既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請1001嘅巴絲開po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8242613aa4887f8507b0d6076331b8032ebeaa26","tid":857653,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:42:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ignore this post</span>"},{"pid":"a487621d57590ae1ddcba01ec2579b140b291d2d","tid":857653,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8242613aa4887f8507b0d6076331b8032ebeaa26","tid":857653,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:42:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ignore this post</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:43:00.000Z","msg":"👌"},{"pid":"3488b208fa7aa2e2d6a0d6dde78373c5a9ec069a","tid":857653,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:49:02.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6ae11d707ed00df2ce99c978a0b2453463d1c4b0","tid":857653,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3488b208fa7aa2e2d6a0d6dde78373c5a9ec069a","tid":857653,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:49:02.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83d4c60efbcd51adcc56d37f8ea8f91260d9752","tid":857653,"uid":175077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"19618fdf19cb3e647bf503472569f3704f22f055","tid":857653,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e83d4c60efbcd51adcc56d37f8ea8f91260d9752","tid":857653,"uid":175077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"hi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee67bdd52d9c9bcc4ba5f7c6f6ab2cff09830d19","tid":857653,"uid":175077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5240378afb898fbcac644393b48243a99550b592","tid":857653,"uid":175077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19618fdf19cb3e647bf503472569f3704f22f055","tid":857653,"ui